schools.name: Pioneer Magnet School for the Visual and Performing Arts

data.description: Delightful 3 bdrm, 2 bth Pioneer home with over a 1/2 acre of useable outdoor space!  This bright home has been well loved and is move in ready.  Interior has great touches including kitchen and bathroom updates, laminate flooring, private master bedroom with beautiful tile shower in master bath, laundry room and much more!  Outdoors enjoy the beautiful deck and patio areas.  Newer roof and deck! Enjoy gardening?  Large and sunny side yard with a fenced off garden box area, plus plenty of space for your outdoor projects!  Extra storage under home. Under 5 minutes to shopping, and approx. 45 mins to Kirkwood Ski Resort!
